# driftmd web — production URL

The deployed frontend is **https://driftmd.vercel.app** (Vercel).

When discussing or implementing anything about the **live site**, **public links**, **deployment verification**, or **what users see in production**, use that URL—not a placeholder and not localhost unless the task is explicitly about local dev (`next dev`).

- Source for the site: monorepo path `packages/web` (Next.js App Router).
- After changes that affect the public site, assume deployment goes through the Vercel project connected to this repo (typically production branch `main`).
